                                                <h2 class="main-head" style="text-align:left; padding-top:20px;">
                                                    Code Of Ethics
                                                </h2>
                                                <div class="content_text" style="text-align:justify;padding: 0;">
                                                    For promoting productivity and intellectual output and honesty in
                                                    academic writing, MES Kalladi College has taken immense number of
                                                    measures for maintaining ethical practices in research activities.
                                                    The guidelines of the procedures has to be abide by the students and
                                                    teachers for their excellence in research by the following :
                                                    <br/>
                                                    <br/>
                                                    <ul>
                                                        <li>
                                                            All research and academic works of the students such as
                                                            assignment, project reports, dissertations should be free
                                                            from plagiarism.
                                                        </li>
                                                        <li>
                                                            Students shall give an undertaking that their project/
                                                            dissertation/ assignment submitted for assessment is
                                                            bonafide and has not been published anywhere for any other
                                                            degree
                                                        </li>
                                                        <li>
                                                            It is the duty of the supervising faculty to check and
                                                            verify that the submitted assignments are free from
                                                            plagiarism before issuing the certificate to the student.
                                                        </li>
                                                        <li>
                                                            To ensure the authenticity of the projects/theses
                                                            /dissertations submitted the students and faculty members
                                                            may use the Plagiarism Checker software provided in the
                                                            library .
                                                        </li>
                                                        <li>
                                                            Research Promotion Council arranges awareness and
                                                            sensitization programmes on Plagiarism for the students and
                                                            faculties
                                                        </li>
                                                        <li>
                                                            The Research guides and their Research scholars of our
                                                            Institution can access the plagiarism check software using
                                                            Username and Password provided by the University of Calicut.
                                                        </li>
                                                    </ul>

